The paper deals with face analysis using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multi-task learning and regularization techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves smile detection and age estimation, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) respectively.
